  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168060/extras/62d4405b78622b347cc14d985f39bd92.poster.avif?t=1752171297\" width=792 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168060/extras/62d4405b78622b347cc14d985f39bd92.webm?t=1752171297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168060/extras/62d4405b78622b347cc14d985f39bd92.mp4?t=1752171297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the King of the Fallen Kingdom, once a mighty ruler whose realm was destroyed by treacherous betrayal. Now, you find yourself in hell, surrounded by demonic entities and malevolent creatures, where every day is a struggle for survival. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But you don’t just want to survive. You seek a way to return to the mortal realm and restore your kingdom. Gather allies and useful items while fighting through hordes of enemies for the chance of escape.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ items </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique boss fights  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 item/weapon slots  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different playstyles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Fast runs (15-30 minutes)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168060/extras/02f04cc20f7654f1d962a814d95e12ee.poster.avif?t=1752171297\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168060/extras/02f04cc20f7654f1d962a814d95e12ee.webm?t=1752171297\" 